p.seg:
With these witnesses: Geoffrey, abbot of Dunfermline; Alured, abbot of Stirling;
                  Robert, prior of St Andrews; Samson and Alan, monks of
                  Durham; Thorald, the archdeacon; Aiulf, the dean; Geoffrey of Lasswade; Master Andrew; Adam and
                     Richard, the bishop’s chaplains; Geoffrey, the clerk;
                     Peter of Stirling; and the full synod.
